We use Ansible to manage our server configuration. This is our Ansible
repository.

Decadegraphy is an open project. So we decided to make our configuration
public as well, just like what Wikimedia Foudation does.


Links:
- Decadegraphy: https://github.com/decadegraphy/decadegraphy
- Server configuration of WMF: https://github.com/wikimedia/puppet
